<body>
<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1361542" n="1"/>
                        <opener><salute><lb/>Viro <abbr>Illustr.</abbr> et <abbr>Doctiss.</abbr> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-119166895">Nicolao Bernoull<choice><orig><g ref="#j">j</g></orig><reg>i</reg></choice></rs>
                        <lb/><rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-102552517">Petrus <abbr>Ant.<hi rend="sup">us</hi></abbr> Michelotti</rs> <abbr>S. P. D.</abbr></salute></opener>
                        <p><lb/>Quod m<choice><orig><g ref="#ehat">√™</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice>as acceperis <rs type="letter" key="B_1718-12-19_991170517038805501">literas</rs> quas <choice><abbr>a. d.</abbr><expan>a dato</expan></choice> <date when="1718-12-19">19 hujus mensis</date>
                              <lb/>ad Te dedi nequaquam dubito. Ad Te hodie scribendi
                        <lb/>nova mihi suboritur occasio. In <rs type="letter" key="B_1717-10-17_991170515153305501">literis</rs> quas ab <abbr>Illustr.</abbr>
                        <lb/><rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118509969">Patruo Tuo</rs> jampridem accepi moram mihi injiciit
                              <lb/>h<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>c propositio. <choice><orig><g ref="#quote">‚Äû</g></orig><reg></reg></choice><cit><quote>Vires centripet<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>, quibus corpora gyran<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/><choice><orig><g ref="#quote">‚Äû</g></orig><reg></reg></choice>tia in circumferentiis retinentur sunt in composi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/><choice><orig><g ref="#quote">‚Äû</g></orig><reg></reg></choice>ta ratione ex quadratis velocitatum, et ex simplici reci<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/><choice><orig><g ref="#quote">‚Äû</g></orig><reg></reg></choice>proca diametrorum, hoc est, ex simplici directa con<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/><choice><orig><g ref="#quote">‚Äû</g></orig><reg></reg></choice>vexitatum, seu flexurarum.</quote></cit></p>
<p><lb/>Peto a Te hujus Theorematis demonstrationem
                              <lb/>uti etiam ejus rei quod convexitates seu curva<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tur<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> sint semper diametris reciproce propor<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tionales.</p>
<p><lb/>Ejusmodi propositionis beneficio vult demonstrare
                        <lb/><abbr>Celeber.</abbr> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118509969">Patruus</rs> male dixisse <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118587544">Newtonum</rs> quando 
                        <lb/>in <rs type="biblio" key="biblio_KGWAEINJ">Optic.</rs> scripsit <cit><quote><choice><orig><g ref="#quote">‚Äû</g></orig><reg></reg></choice>Attractionem radii luminis
                        <lb/><choice><orig><g ref="#quote">‚Äû</g></orig><reg></reg></choice>pro quantitate materi<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> su<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> esse ad gravitatem
                        <lb/><choice><orig><g ref="#quote">‚Äû</g></orig><reg></reg></choice>quam corpus aliquod projectum habet pro quantitate
                        <lb/><choice><orig><g ref="#quote">‚Äû</g></orig><reg></reg></choice>ibidem materi<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> su<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>, in composita ratione veloci<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/><choice><orig><g ref="#quote">‚Äû</g></orig><reg></reg></choice>tatis radii luminis ad velocitatem corporis illius projecti,
                              <lb/>et flexur<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>, seu curvatur<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> line<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>, quam radius describit. De<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/><choice><orig><g ref="#quote">‚Äû</g></orig><reg></reg></choice>buisse enim dicere ait in composita ratione ex duplicata
                        <lb/><choice><orig><g ref="#quote">‚Äû</g></orig><reg></reg></choice>velocitatis radii ad velocitatem corporis projecti, et ex sim<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/><choice><orig><g ref="#quote">‚Äû</g></orig><reg></reg></choice>plici flexur<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> in loco refractionis ad flexuram, quam
                              <pb facs="1361543" n="2"/>
                        <lb/><choice><orig><g ref="#quote">‚Äû</g></orig><reg></reg></choice>corpus projectum describit, si videlicet inclinatio radii
                        <lb/><choice><orig><g ref="#quote">‚Äû</g></orig><reg></reg></choice>ad superficiem refringentem eadem sit qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> corporis
                        <lb/><choice><orig><g ref="#quote">‚Äû</g></orig><reg></reg></choice>illius projecti ad horizontem.</quote></cit></p>
<p><lb/>Hac autem occasione Te rogo ut consideres an h<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>c
                        <lb/><rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118587544">Newtoniana</rs> propositio vera sit. <cit><quote><choice><orig><g ref="#quote">‚Äû</g></orig><reg></reg></choice>Eorum corporum
                        <lb/><choice><orig><g ref="#quote">‚Äû</g></orig><reg></reg></choice>qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> sunt ejusdem generis et virtutis quanto est quod<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/><choice><orig><g ref="#quote">‚Äû</g></orig><reg></reg></choice>que minutius tanto fortiorem habet pro ratione
                        <lb/><choice><orig><g ref="#quote">‚Äû</g></orig><reg></reg></choice>magnitudinis su<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> vim attrahentem.</quote></cit></p>
<p><lb/>Spero ut valeas et strenue pergas non tam in
      <lb/>responsione paranda <rs type="person">Nebuloni</rs><note type="comment">Siehe dazu die Fussnote im <rs type="letter" key="B_1718-11-20_991170517051005501">Brief</rs> von Niclaus I Bernoulli an A. Michelotti vom 20.11.1718.</note> responsione
                              <lb/>indigno quam in perficiendo comendoque eximio
                        <lb/>operi mathematico, de quo toties Te rogavi, et
                              <lb/>Te continenter rogabo non tantum pro publico
                              <lb/>bono, et mea utilitate,<del>quo</del> sed pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>cipue
                              <lb/>pro tuo honore, et gloria. Hic enim et istic
      <lb/>imo vero tota <rs type="place" key="place_KON-italie">Italia</rs> nisi aliquod opus publice<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tur non credunt <rs type="person">Hominem</rs> aliquem tametsi
                              <lb/>doctissimum esse sapientem. Saltem ultimis
                        <lb/>Bachanaliorum diebus, et citius si poteris Te <rs type="place" key="place_VER-repven">domi
                              <lb/>me<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> expecto, ubi de compluribus rebus verba
                              <lb/>faciemus.</p> <closer><salute>Interim vale, et me amare perge.</salute>
                                                      <lb/>Dabam <rs type="place" key="place_VER-repven">Venetiis</rs> <choice><abbr>a. d.</abbr><expan>a dato</expan></choice> <date when="1718-12-22">22 <abbr>X<hi rend="sup">bris</hi></abbr> 1718</date><supplied>.</supplied></closer>
                        <postscript><p><lb/><abbr>P. S.</abbr>
                                                <lb/>Scribo hodie ad <abbr>Ill.</abbr> <abbr>D.</abbr> Marchionem <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-11887733X">Polenum</rs>, quem ut sa<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>lutes rogo.</p></postscript>
</div>
